Common.Highlight.Common.Text: 61,000 SF total office space in a one-story building
Located in Carmel, Indiana - home to several large corporate headquarters
Newest addition to 35 acre mixed-use Lakeside Development
Adjacent to new retail center, Lakeside Shops (10,273 SF of retail available)
Tenants can use the fitness center, workout facility and basketball court located in the clubhouse near the entrance of the adjacent apartment community

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located in Carmel, Indiana, Lakeside Green Business Center is the newest addition to the 35-acre mixed-use Carmel Lakeside Development and is adjacent to new retail center, Lakeside Shops. Lakeside Green in located within minutes of major developments in Midtown Carmel, the Proscenium and Carmel City Center.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Premier Class A office space available in Carmel, Indiana. Lakeside Green is LEED Gold Certified and has a geothermal HVAC. Lakeside Green boasts ample parking, showers and restrooms. It is the newest addition to 35 acre mixed-use Lakeside Development. 5,694 SF space available for sublease on first floor, term through 05/31/2024.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Class A Carmel Office Space | LEED Gold Certified | Lakeside Green Business Center

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Meridian Park Place is a single story Class A office building nestled in a beautiful wooded setting within the city of Carmel, Indiana.
Owner and property manager on site
Abundant area amenities including restaurants, banks, hotels, and retail
Close proximity to Ritz Charles Carmel an elegant catering & conference center
Signage opportunty at Meridian Park Place Two

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located off of U.S. 31, Meridian Park Place is within minutes of abundant shopping, retail, hotels and banks. The office buildings are nestled in a beautiful wooded setting with close proximity to the Ritz Charles, which offers elegant catering and conference centers. The property is only 3 minutes to I-465.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Class A office and medical space for lease in Carmel, Indiana on U.S. 31. Meridian Park Place boasts on-site management, abundant area amenities and a signage opportunity. It is within close proximity to the Ritz Charles which offers elegant catering and a conference center. Meridian Park Place Two offers a signage opportunity facing U.S. 31.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Class A Office and Medical Space Available | Signage Opportunity on U.S. 31 | Meridian Park Place
